Privacy Policy
--------------

Applies to the use of Tayasui Websites and Apps.
This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data when you use our Apps and Websites. 
___________________________________


For our Apps containing a Community
-----------------------------------
(Tayasui Sketches and Tayasui Sketches Pro but not Tayasui Sketches School, Tayasui Color, Tayasui Doodle Book and Drawing Carl) :

We collect, only if you post to the community : 
The email address and Name, as you enter them in the App.

This data will only be used to enable us to contact a user of the Community if we need to do so.
For example, to propose him/her a feature on our sites or social networks.

____________________________________

For all other Tayasui applications : 
-----------------------------------

We may collect Personal Data like : 
The type of mobile device you use, your mobile device unique ID, your mobile operating system, unique device identifiers and other diagnostic data.

We may uses the collected data for this purposes:
To notify you about changes to our Service
To provide customer support
To monitor the usage of the App
To detect and address technical issues

____________________________________
Changes : 
Tayasui reserves the right to make amendments to this Privacy Policy at any time. If you have objections to the Privacy Policy, you should not access or use the Sites or the Applications.

____________________________________
Contact Us: 
If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us at sketches.help@gmail.com

This privacy policy was last updated on September 2nd, 2020.